{"tid":2021241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我畫野唔叻 但都畫左好多文宣片","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:30:35.000Z","uid":263423,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63caf3d60da02e583b43be233b875a1f972fea24","tid":2021241,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"[代Po]<br />\n雖然我無連登AC，但之前抗爭好激個陣我都成日係連登睇Po<br />\n隨著抗爭嘅熱度下降，我少左嚟連登睇Po<br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭嘅風險好大，最近一段時間我做左一啲抗爭文宣嘅片<br />\n希望大家可以支持下，中意嘅話可以訂閱<br />\n過多陣就要選舉啦，我會繼續創作，參與文宣戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f19V3JbMkY8&amp;t=8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df19V3JbMkY8%26t%3D8s&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=afbea0ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f19V3JbMkY8&amp;t=8s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yIV6vmzm5hw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyIV6vmzm5hw&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=4ecefda3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yIV6vmzm5hw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m4SavJ0VfXA&amp;t=4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm4SavJ0VfXA%26t%3D4s&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=0bc046e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m4SavJ0VfXA&amp;t=4s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0u0I0WaCV4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0u0I0WaCV4g&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=ef252685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0u0I0WaCV4g</a><br />\n<br />\n多得手足Nickole Fish設計嘅紙娃娃系統<br />\n先令我很醜嘅畫工，得以提升水平<br />\n<br />\n但好遺憾嘅係是Nickole Fish設計嘅紙娃娃系統<br />\n因為受到大陸五毛嘅舉報<br />\n被相關嘅日本公司下左架<br />\n抗爭被打壓，香港人被迫害嘅命運持續<br />\n<br />\n最最勇武嘅人，可能都入左監獄<br />\n逃亡離開了香港，甚至失去了生命<br />\n<br />\n但一切仲未結束，我唔想手足嘅犧牲同付出白費<br />\n我們團隊只能盡力創作，雖然比唔上好多藝術級嘅設計<br />\n但都希望仍然有鬥志嘅抗爭嘅手足幫忙分享<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LU32tzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLU32tzG.jpg&h=8091e712&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32fc33efeaf4460f19a8eedc7f3b00d099afe0a2","tid":2021241,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"698c674a32e3b5438f31f5da48ffd2687b5733c2","tid":2021241,"uid":131667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb056ddb13986e07d1113fc7f1b9883a6a4f860f","tid":2021241,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44442c8675a66bf250466e07f47cb1526e5ef641","tid":2021241,"uid":274542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"Liked"},{"pid":"e75ec8b5ab21bd47ab1659a6ad4f24032c69a64f","tid":2021241,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}